# PM Interpretation

The interviews suggest that TechMPower should be managed as a complex service-delivery ecosystem rather than a standalone intervention rollout.

The highest-priority PM concerns are therefore:

- workflow reliability
- stakeholder coordination
- operational adoption
- implementation scalability
- continuity of care
- monitoring and feedback loops
- adaptation to local operational constraints

The project’s success depends less on a single intervention component and more on whether the surrounding implementation ecosystem functions consistently over time.

