# Recommended Product Priorities

The evidence suggests several implementation priorities:

1. Standardize coordination workflows across organizations
2. Improve staff onboarding and training systems
3. Build stronger transition workflows between jail and community care
4. Establish continuous monitoring and support processes
5. Reduce operational friction in transportation and follow-up coordination
6. Ensure technology adoption aligns with local workflow realities

